rest_of_day_open: I AM SO EXCITED FOR MY WEEKEND! So I have Occipital and Trigeminal Neuralgia, which suck big time. I got nerve blocks yesterday and I feel like a completely new person right now! I can only get the blocks every 3 months and they only last a couple weeks. I can actually go out with my friends, go shopping, visit family, get in a decent workout, and pretty much do anything besides lie in bed and hope I'm put out of my misery.
